-- Sony to Buy Seiko Epson’s Chinese LCD Unit for 775 Million Yuan
-- B y   K y u n g   B o k   C h o
-- 2011-02-02T06:10:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-02/sony-to-acquire-seiko-epson-s-chinese-liquid-crystal-display-unit.html
  Sony Corp . agreed to acquire  Seiko
Epson Corp .’s Chinese liquid-crystal-display subsidiary for 775
million yuan ($118 million). The transaction will be completed
in the first half of the year ending March 31, 2012, according
to statements today on the Japanese companies’ websites.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kyung Bok Cho at 
